168
00:13:54,009 --> 00:13:55,069
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">要出门？</font>

169
00:13:55,739 --> 00:13:57,959
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你不是喜欢吃更甜的苹果吗</font>

170
00:14:01,679 --> 00:14:04,419
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">怎么了？为什么要笑？</font>

171
00:14:06,279 --> 00:14:09,359
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你也太喜欢我了吧？</font>

172
00:14:10,939 --> 00:14:12,919
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不是 你这也太莫名其妙了吧</font>

173
00:14:16,079 --> 00:14:19,209
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">没想到你会动摇成这样啊</font>

174
00:14:21,359 --> 00:14:23,529
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">烦死了 笨蛋！</font>

175
00:14:29,259 --> 00:14:32,939
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">该死 我再也不会惯着她了</font>

176
00:14:51,049 --> 00:14:52,859
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">该怎么办呢…</font>

177
00:15:00,649 --> 00:15:05,279
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">好久没遇到这种日常生活中的小灾难了</font>

178
00:15:16,989 --> 00:15:18,129
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">原来如此</font>

179
00:15:21,319 --> 00:15:23,639
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我要有危险了</font>

180
00:15:24,919 --> 00:15:26,089
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">啊？</font>

181
00:15:28,619 --> 00:15:30,919
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我要有危险了</font>

182
00:15:31,479 --> 00:15:35,429
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">虽然有强烈的不祥预感 但还是先问清楚吧</font>

183
00:15:36,029 --> 00:15:37,739
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">谁会给你带来危险啊？</font>

184
00:15:38,719 --> 00:15:40,039
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">就是你啊！</font>

185
00:15:41,019 --> 00:15:46,299
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">就算你能得到我的人 也休想得到我的心！</font>

186
00:15:46,379 --> 00:15:50,389
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">一上来就给我扣这种莫名其妙的罪名 太不讲道理了吧</font>

187
00:15:50,959 --> 00:15:54,489
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">抱歉 我对小鬼头没兴趣</font>

188
00:15:55,549 --> 00:15:57,369
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你说谁是小鬼头啊！</font>

189
00:15:59,329 --> 00:16:02,079
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你这表现得够明显的了 先冷静一下</font>

190
00:16:02,859 --> 00:16:05,199
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这种时候要先做个自我介绍</font>

191
00:16:06,949 --> 00:16:10,029
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我的名字叫君冢君彦 你呢？</font>

192
00:16:11,289 --> 00:16:12,299
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我是…</font>

193
00:16:14,249 --> 00:16:15,339
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">艾丽西亚？</font>

194
00:16:16,159 --> 00:16:20,089
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">为什么是疑问句 你难道是从什么仙境来的吗？
(艾丽西亚(Alicia)这个名字属于爱丽丝(Alice)的变形，
出自《爱丽丝漫游仙境》。)</font>

195
00:16:20,739 --> 00:16:21,869
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我肚子饿了</font>

196
00:16:23,929 --> 00:16:26,199
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你讲话可真是天马行空</font>

197
00:16:29,959 --> 00:16:30,859
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">好吃吗？</font>

198
00:16:31,419 --> 00:16:34,039
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">嗯 好甜 好好吃</font>

199
00:16:36,639 --> 00:16:39,769
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">等等 你都吃光了？</font>

200
00:16:41,609 --> 00:16:43,439
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">对了 这里是什么地方？</font>

201
00:16:43,609 --> 00:16:48,089
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">还问这里是什么地方？不是你自己决定睡在这里的吗</font>

202
00:16:50,629 --> 00:16:51,599
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不知道</font>

203
00:16:53,599 --> 00:16:55,209
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">失忆？</font>

204
00:16:55,549 --> 00:16:56,169
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">嗯？</font>

205
00:16:57,069 --> 00:16:58,619
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你还记得什么？</font>

206
00:17:01,139 --> 00:17:04,769
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">只记得我今年17岁</font>

207
00:17:05,839 --> 00:17:08,189
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这绝对是你的误会 赶快忘掉</font>

208
00:17:10,569 --> 00:17:12,199
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你看着什么地方说的啊！</font>

209
00:17:14,539 --> 00:17:19,169
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">本以为只是离家出走 但感觉比我想的要麻烦多了</font>

210
00:17:20,279 --> 00:17:22,499
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">先去找警察吧</font>

211
00:17:40,349 --> 00:17:42,059
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">助手？你回来了？</font>

212
00:17:42,589 --> 00:17:43,849
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">嗯…</font>

213
00:17:45,049 --> 00:17:46,819
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">喂 你在干什么？</font>

214
00:17:47,489 --> 00:17:52,829
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">想做个苹果派 毕竟你特地去买苹果了嘛</font>

215
00:17:55,369 --> 00:17:57,799
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那个…听我说 谢丝塔</font>

216
00:17:58,329 --> 00:17:59,469
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">其实…</font>

217
00:17:59,719 --> 00:18:06,789
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我感受到了你的孺慕之情 那我也有点责任了</font>

218
00:18:07,199 --> 00:18:09,539
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">所以这点事情还是要帮你做一下的</font>

219
00:18:12,199 --> 00:18:13,579
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">对了 苹果呢？</font>

220
00:18:15,949 --> 00:18:17,209
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">其实呢…</font>

221
00:18:17,309 --> 00:18:18,699
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">君冢！</font>

222
00:18:21,609 --> 00:18:23,609
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">有没有小一点的浴巾啊？</font>

223
00:18:35,879 --> 00:18:36,999
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我报警了</font>

224
00:18:39,959 --> 00:18:41,589
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">情况我了解了</font>

225
00:18:42,239 --> 00:18:44,789
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">大吉岭啊 真香</font>

226
00:18:45,179 --> 00:18:47,829
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">嗯 和苹果派很配的哦</font>

227
00:18:49,499 --> 00:18:53,769
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你以后不要妄想能看到我穿围裙的样子了</font>

228
00:18:54,039 --> 00:18:55,959
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">喂喂 别开玩笑啦</font>

229
00:18:56,079 --> 00:18:59,199
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那可是我人生的唯一乐趣了 这样我可是很伤心的</font>

230
00:19:01,489 --> 00:19:04,689
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不 我错了 以后一定会补偿你的！</font>

231
00:19:05,089 --> 00:19:07,839
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这个没有苹果的苹果派真好吃</font>

232
00:19:08,199 --> 00:19:09,209
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">喂！</font>

233
00:19:10,099 --> 00:19:14,509
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">话说 一开始就把她带来找我不就好了</font>

234
00:19:14,719 --> 00:19:19,199
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">遇到迷路的失忆女孩 这才是侦探该出场的时候</font>

235
00:19:20,119 --> 00:19:21,269
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">的确</font>

236
00:19:22,139 --> 00:19:27,079
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你说你叫艾丽西亚对吧 真的连自己的真名都不记得？</font>

237
00:19:27,229 --> 00:19:31,109
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">嗯 只记得今年17岁</font>

238
00:19:31,369 --> 00:19:32,909
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">原来如此 7岁</font>

239
00:19:32,909 --> 00:19:34,209
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">17！</font>

240
00:19:34,759 --> 00:19:38,199
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">认真来说 应该就是12到13岁这样吧</font>

241
00:19:38,379 --> 00:19:40,919
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这是从小腿肚的发育情况得出的结论</font>

242
00:19:41,199 --> 00:19:44,619
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不要在这里展现你的特殊爱好</font>

243
00:19:45,839 --> 00:19:52,969
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">艾丽西亚 我们会负责查出你的身份 但这可不是免费的</font>

244
00:19:53,279 --> 00:19:56,459
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">喂 谢丝塔 你要找小孩子要钱吗</font>

245
00:19:56,819 --> 00:20:00,459
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">和这无关 小孩子也是人啊</font>

246
00:20:00,869 --> 00:20:05,119
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">而且 我觉得无偿的善意是世界上最信不过的东西</font>

247
00:20:05,339 --> 00:20:07,079
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">也对哦</font>

248
00:20:07,499 --> 00:20:09,279
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那我该做什么？</font>

249
00:20:09,759 --> 00:20:13,889
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我希望艾丽西亚能代替我做侦探的工作</font>

250
00:20:14,519 --> 00:20:16,849
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">做侦探的工作？</font>

251
00:20:17,189 --> 00:20:21,229
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">谢丝塔 你也太强人所难了吧</font>

252
00:20:21,669 --> 00:20:23,179
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但是…</font>

253
00:20:24,689 --> 00:20:28,489
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">原来如此 大侦探歇业了啊</font>

254
00:20:28,839 --> 00:20:33,669
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但即使如此 让我来当侦探 艾丽西亚当助手不是更好</font>

255
00:20:33,799 --> 00:20:38,419
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不 你看 毕竟你长着一张助手脸嘛</font>

256
00:20:38,829 --> 00:20:40,209
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不讲道理啊</font>

257
00:20:40,919 --> 00:20:45,079
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">既然接下这个工作 我就会为你提供衣食住</font>

258
00:20:45,829 --> 00:20:49,629
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但是一上来就要当侦探 我没什么自信啊</font>

259
00:20:50,319 --> 00:20:53,989
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">当了侦探就能把助手当成仆人随意使唤了哦</font>

260
00:20:54,089 --> 00:20:57,609
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">太棒了 我干！我要当大侦探！</font>

261
00:20:57,609 --> 00:20:59,749
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">真是一场肮脏的交易</font>

262
00:21:00,029 --> 00:21:03,529
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那我具体要做什么…</font>

263
00:21:05,019 --> 00:21:07,999
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">开膛手杰克似乎复活了</font>

264
00:21:08,919 --> 00:21:13,359
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">风靡小姐？怎么回事 你不是回日本了吗？</font>

265
00:21:13,559 --> 00:21:16,279
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">嗯 想起还有些事要做</font>

266
00:21:16,859 --> 00:21:17,969
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">话说…</font>

267
00:21:18,889 --> 00:21:21,189
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你们什么时候还生孩子了？</font>

268
00:21:21,499 --> 00:21:23,209
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">-你眼瞎啦 -你眼瞎吧</font>

269
00:21:25,429 --> 00:21:28,489
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">话说 开膛手杰克复活是怎么回事？</font>

270
00:21:29,129 --> 00:21:29,969
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">哦</font>

271
00:21:30,259 --> 00:21:35,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">昨天又有被挖走心脏的人出现了 和之前的案子手法相似</font>

272
00:21:35,739 --> 00:21:39,159
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">怎么可能 刻耳柏洛斯当时已经…</font>

273
00:21:42,649 --> 00:21:43,519
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">赫尔</font>

274
00:21:45,709 --> 00:21:49,869
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">其实有一个情报 可能对你们抓住那家伙有帮助</font>

275
00:21:50,689 --> 00:21:52,859
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">虽然还只是个传闻吧</font>

276
00:21:53,339 --> 00:21:57,509
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">据说这个城市里有可以击败SPES的东西</font>

277
00:21:58,049 --> 00:22:00,389
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">而有人将那东西…</font>

278
00:22:01,529 --> 00:22:03,889
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">称为「蓝宝石之眼」</font>

279
00:22:06,589 --> 00:22:11,809
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">每次醒来 你都在我身边</font>

280
00:22:11,959 --> 00:22:17,109
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">给我一个全新的早晨</font>

281
00:22:17,109 --> 00:22:22,489
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那心跳是如此温柔</font>

282
00:22:22,489 --> 00:22:27,459
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">却又悲伤得催人泪下</font>

283
00:22:27,809 --> 00:22:33,089
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">在大声叫喊着 想要见到某人</font>

284
00:22:33,159 --> 00:22:38,489
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">却又不知道名字和长相</font>

285
00:22:38,489 --> 00:22:43,809
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但我真的听到了那声音</font>

286
00:22:43,809 --> 00:22:48,379
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">只能漫无目的地去探寻</font>

287
00:22:48,769 --> 00:22:54,059
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">虽然可能只会徒增烦恼</font>

288
00:22:54,109 --> 00:23:02,149
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但这不是为了别人而是为了自己</font>

289
00:23:03,949 --> 00:23:09,249
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">胸膛中的声音 那声呐喊 指引着我前进</font>

290
00:23:09,249 --> 00:23:14,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">将零落的心意捡起 送到它想去的地方吧</font>

291
00:23:14,569 --> 00:23:19,819
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">因为是你告诉我生命的意义</font>

292
00:23:19,819 --> 00:23:27,839
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">让我觉得 这个世界也许还没那么坏</font>

293
00:23:36,008 --> 00:23:41,018
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">(第7集 将来，你总会回想起这一天)</font>

